n in both criminal and civil cases.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997235837231409, \"rank\": 0.00027645079581302905, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The threat\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"legal action\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"opinion\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"robust protection\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"both criminal and civil cases\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In France, however, free speech is in a free fall with the left pushing for the censorship and criminalization of an ever-expanding range of political and religious speech.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 861, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.7093529270496738, \"rank\": 0.2371737259469038, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"free speech\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 889}, {\"ngram\": \"a free fall\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"the censorship\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"criminalization\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"an ever-expanding range\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"political and religious speech\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony itself had some truly powerful and stunning elements.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ceremony\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"some truly powerful and stunning elements\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I enjoyed the mix of music and imagery as well as the effort to show the diversity of France.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.597015775533367, \"rank\": 0.658921610016917, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mix\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"imagery\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"the effort\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"the diversity\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, other elements were more divisive or excessive.\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other elements\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, the producers decided to use the ceremony to feature such elements as three young people hooking up for a \\\"m\\u00e9nage \\u00e0 trois.\\\"\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"the producers\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"such elements\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"three young people\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"m\\u00e9nage \\u00e0 trois\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With many families watching with kids, many of us thought the scene was inappropriate for such an event.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many families\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1455}, {\"ngram\": \"such an event\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it was the supper scene that led to protests from clerics and critics.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the supper scene\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"protests\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"clerics\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"critics\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While claiming a message of \\\"tolerance,\\\" the scene was taken as yet another slap at religious elements in society.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"tolerance\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"yet another slap\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"religious elements\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is a debate that has continued to rage, particularly on the Internet.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a debate\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"the Internet\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Audrey Msellati, Butch's attorney, posted a statement on Butch'sInstagram accountthat the DJ and activist will seek legal action after being \\\"the target of an extremely violent campaign of cyber-harassment and defamation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1765, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Horne\", \"score\": 0.993612004800474, \"rank\": 0.006428994070227525, \"text\": \"Audrey\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Horne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Horne\"}, {\